Package: spectralAnomaly
Type: Package
Title: Detect Anomalies Using the 'Spectral Residual' Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Apply the 'Spectral Residual' algorithm to data, such as a
    time series, to detect anomalies. Anomaly scores can be used determine 
    outliers based upon a threshold or fed into more sophistcated prediction models.
